<div class="header">
<a class="title" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/commit/da8c86dd8be244100da226a11b416c20d0c914d6">avcodec/cfhd: Keep track of which subbands have been read</a>
</div>
<div class="title_text">
<table class="object_header">
<tr><td>author</td><td><a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/da8c86dd8be244100da226a11b416c20d0c914d6?s=Michael+Niedermayer;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by Michael Niedermayer">Michael Niedermayer</a> <a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/da8c86dd8be244100da226a11b416c20d0c914d6?s=michael@niedermayer.cc;st=author" title="Search for commits authored by michael@niedermayer.cc">&lt;michael@niedermayer.cc&gt;</a></td><td rowspan="2"></td></tr>
<tr><td></td><td><span class="datetime">Sat, 3 Apr 2021 14:04:48 +0000</span> (16:04 +0200)</td></tr>
<tr><td>committer</td><td><a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/da8c86dd8be244100da226a11b416c20d0c914d6?s=Michael+Niedermayer;st=committer" title="Search for commits committed by Michael Niedermayer">Michael Niedermayer</a> <a class="list" href="/gitweb/ffmpeg.git/search/da8c86dd8be244100da226a11b416c20d0c914d6?s=michael@niedermayer.cc;st=committer" title="Search for commits committed by michael@niedermayer.cc">&lt;michael@niedermayer.cc&gt;</a></td><td rowspan="2"></td></tr>
